olor);\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .film-item {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Crimson Reels Film Festival</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Celebrate the Art of Cinema</h2>\n            <p>Experience a diverse selection of captivating films, from groundbreaking independent features to stunning international shorts.</p>\n            <a href=\"#schedule\" class=\"cta-button\">View Schedule</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About the Festival</h2>\n            <p>Crimson Reels is dedicated to showcasing emerging talent and celebrating the rich tapestry of global cinema. Join us for an unforgettable journey through stories that inspire, challenge, and entertain.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"featured-films\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Films</h2>\n            <div class=\"film-list\">\n                <div class=\"film-item\">\n                    <h3>The Scarlet Letter</h3>\n                    <p>A gripping drama exploring themes of love, betrayal, and societal judgment in a historical setting.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"film-item\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Dawn</h3>\n                    <p>An action-packed thriller with breathtaking visuals and a story that will keep you on the edge of your seat.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"film-item\">\n                    <h3>Whispers in